"_ _7"></span>如地位、<span class="_ _7"></span>财富、<span class="_ _7"></span>名</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y2ae ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">声、<span class="_ _b"></span>青春等，<span class="_ _a"></span>全部是无常变化的。<span class="_ _b"></span>这是无可争辩的一个事实，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y2af ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">也是非常重要的一种理念。 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
